articles.title: Moldovans cast votes to choose president and decide on EU path as Russian interference claims spike - The Associated Press
articles.description: Moldovans have started casting their ballots in two key votes. Those votes could determine whether the European Union candidate country — which neighbors Ukraine — remains on a pro-Western path amid allegations that Russia has tried to undermine the electoral…
